                            eye donation and how the entire process works. Best infection control practices in hands allow KD Hospital to become one of the best cornea transplant centres in Ahmedabad.
                        </p>
                        <p>A successful cornea transplant allows the individual to recover their eyesight in a few weeks. A corneal transplant gives an option to live an improved quality of life without compromising on vision. </p>
